{"id": 2865, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，做什么事会让你觉得“是在浪费生命”？", "description": "跟着营销号学财务自由。", "record_count": 7359, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201903251728493ASInkNBCwhvjX4G.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-29T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 336384, "content": "和姐妹聚在一起花大量时间嚼舌根 翻来覆去就那几个\"敌人\"", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622591}, {"id": 336640, "content": "刷微博", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528961}, {"id": 335617, "content": "每天毫无目的在淘宝和抖音间来回切换", "image": null, "praise_count": 463, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 336385, "content": "打开各种无聊的界面，关闭，再打开……", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461027}, {"id": 336641, "content": "躺床上玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623367}, {"id": 335618, "content": "和十分合不来的人恋爱，又迟迟拖着不分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 543, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 336386, "content": "看这种不知道有什么用的调查", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1571155}, {"id": 336642, "content": "吃瓜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074638}, {"id": 336898, "content": "走不得不走但又毫无意义的形式", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1625466}, {"id": 335619, "content": "一边做着朝九晚十二的工作一边看健身攻略", "image": null, "praise_count": 139, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 336387, "content": "空想", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680607}, {"id": 336643, "content": "发一条朋友圈，纠结有没有人点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1167646}, {"id": 336899, "content": "应该是玩手机吧，就连睡觉都要把手机放手边", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1625451}, {"id": 336388, "content": "常常关注生活琐事，社交软件代替言语交流，网络媒体代替思考，电视电影代替阅读，常常因为在奋斗的年级无所事事而迷茫", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1583593}, {"id": 336644, "content": "上班摸鱼，日常摸鱼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622422}, {"id": 337924, "content": "不谋财", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631103}, {"id": 336389, "content": "花太多时间在游戏.浏览页面上", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471699}, {"id": 336645, "content": "进行无效沟通的会议", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623394}, {"id": 336390, "content": "不想聊天的人硬拉着你聊天 看到他们打来的电话或信息就觉得回了就是在浪费时间浪费生命", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615113}, {"id": 336646, "content": "做自己不喜欢做的事情，比如做自己不喜欢的工作，这些事是无法反驳，现实就是这。", "image": "img/option/option/20190330093020LvRXrDqN2oV4OEnt", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623316}, {"id": 336391, "content": "开一个没有结果也没有尽头的会…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294190}, {"id": 336647, "content": "堵车吧，对我来说", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126152}, {"id": 336903, "content": "做什么都浪费生命", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613880}, {"id": 336392, "content": "超星尔雅", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602930}, {"id": 336648, "content": "打游戏就是在浪费时间而且没有回报的浪费", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623396}, {"id": 336393, "content": "好像每件事都是在浪费\r\n好像没做什么有意义的事情\r\n都是生活罢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597047}, {"id": 336649, "content": "早晨一觉醒来11点", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623399}, {"id": 336650, "content": "逛了很久的淘宝，啥也没买。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623397}, {"id": 336395, "content": "没啥事干，干啥也没劲，前天刚把微信qq卸载了，清净几天", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010719}, {"id": 336651, "content": "王者荣耀", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548420}, {"id": 337163, "content": "在没找到能给予你快乐的精神支柱前都是对生命的严重浪费。", "image": "img/option/option/20190402201639sf3VDj2pbANydB6F", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626690}, {"id": 336396, "content": "无目的的玩手机\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617388}, {"id": 336652, "content": "做着不喜欢的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403747}, {"id": 335885, "content": "发一条朋友圈，每隔五分钟瞅一眼看有没有人留言", "image": null, "praise_count": 1259, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 336397, "content": "坐着发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622636}, {"id": 336653, "content": "我的大学生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142064}, {"id": 343565, "content": "。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 336398, "content": "删除了除好奇心外所有资讯应用，但每天看好奇心的时间却变长了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118083}, {"id": 336399, "content": "玩手机，很想戒掉但戒不掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615751}, {"id": 336655, "content": "不能专心做自己应该做的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623436}, {"id": 337167, "content": "每天都按时上课，按时吃饭，按时开会……\n一切似乎都在有条不紊地展开\n但我想要什么，我得到了什么\n我不知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626710}, {"id": 336400, "content": "每天在班级里发呆还是发呆，不知不觉，一年过去了，俩年过去了，一辈子玩完了。！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622562}, {"id": 336656, "content": "沉迷综艺娱乐节目，全面娱乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456839}, {"id": 336401, "content": "看没有什么内容的朋友圈，被关系挟持点赞分享。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622134}, {"id": 336657, "content": "现在做的事情都感觉在浪费时间，没有一件让自己有成就感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1584805}, {"id": 336402, "content": "纠结于各种模糊的情感情绪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1597986}, {"id": 336658, "content": "没有节制的玩手机，逛淘宝，刷抖音，玩游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1478569}, {"id": 342290, "content": "做不喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1583920}, {"id": 336403, "content": "学校里的某些活动能不能取消啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681648}, {"id": 336659, "content": "没目标", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623456}]}